title: DerbyCon – Dave Kennedy [ML B-Side]
description: DerbyCon was all about making the community - a family. Dave Kennedy, one of the founders of DerbyCon, talks about the unique vibe of the conference, his fear of clowns,  and why he'll never - NEVER - listen to a Busta Rhymes album again.
